text: Planinica or Planinitsa (Cyrillic: Планиница) may refer to the following places: ==Serbia== * Planinica (Pirot) * Planinica (Zaječar) * Planinica (Mionica) * Planinica (Dimitrovgrad) * Planinica (Trstenik) ==Bosnia and Herzegovina== * Planinica (Bugojno) ==Bulgaria== * Planinitsa, Burgas Province * Planinitsa, Pernik Province
title: Planinica
